--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TO SETUP WHEN CLONING THIS PROJECT:
run command: composer install
edit files : app/etc/db/default.json (db credentials), and etc/Host.php (URL sub-directory, Timezone)
run command: composer setup
run command: sb store users id:1 groups:root,admin password:[replace with password]

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
THE FIRST TIME YOU SETUP THE PROJECT, INSTALL AND COMMIT THE LIBRARIES:
run command: bower install
run command: git add libraries
run command: git commit -am "libraries"
run command: git push

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHEN PULLING NEW CODE:
run command: composer migrate
